       _d_._h_i_s_t_o_g_r_a_m displays the category-value distribution for a  user-speci-
       fied  raster map layer, in the form of a bar chart or a pie chart.  The
       display will be displayed in the active display frame on  the  graphics
       monitor,  using  the colors in the raster map layer's color table.  The
       program determines the raster file's  category  value  distribution  by
       counting cells.

